title: Cheesy Taco Sticks
directions: Preheat oven to 425 degrees and coat a baking sheet with non-stick spray.
Brown ground beef in a skillet, mixing in the taco seasoning in. Don't add water as you usually would, just stir the seasoning until all the ground beef is fully coated.
ingredients: 2 colby jack and cheddar cheese sticks, halved
